&lt;p&gt;CS168 looks for ideas (1) that are non-obvious, (2) conceptually simple, and (3)
fundamental in the sense that you&amp;rsquo;ll likely use them.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Prefix Sum</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/prefix-sum/</link><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/prefix-sum/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;dfn&gt;prefix sum&lt;/dfn&gt;, &lt;dfn&gt;cumulative sum&lt;/dfn&gt;, or simply
&lt;dfn&gt;scan&lt;/dfn&gt; of a sequence of numbers \(x_0, x_1, x_2, &amp;hellip;\) is a
second sequence of numbers \(y_0, y_1, y_2, &amp;hellip;\), the sums of
prefixes (running totals) of the input sequence, e.g., \(y_2 = x_0 +
x_1 + x_2\). Prefix sums are trivially computable as \(y_i = y_{i-1} +
x_i\). Prefix sum may be generalized to any binary operation, e.g.,
using multiplication instead of addition generates the sequence of
factorial numbers instead of triangular numbers. &lt;span class="citation-ref"&gt;&lt;a href="#prefixSumWiki"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Fourth-Wall</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/fourth-wall/</link><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/fourth-wall/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Messiah-Mythos</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/messiah-mythos/</link><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/messiah-mythos/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Civil-Rights-Movement</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/civil-rights-movement/</link><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/civil-rights-movement/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Change-Motif</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/change-motif/</link><pubDate>Sat, 30 Sep 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/change-motif/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Death-Motif</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/death-motif/</link><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jul 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/death-motif/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Divinity-Motif</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/divinity-motif/</link><pubDate>Mon, 29 May 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/divinity-motif/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Justice-Motif</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/justice-motif/</link><pubDate>Mon, 29 May 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/justice-motif/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Supergirl</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/supergirl/</link><pubDate>Mon, 29 May 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/tags/supergirl/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Databases</title>